225  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_id(
226      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
227      const unsigned char* endp,
228      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
229    uint32_t index;
230    llparse_match_t res;
231    index = s->_index;
232    for (; p != endp; p++) {
233      unsigned char current;
234      current = *p;
235      if (current == seq[index]) {
236        if (++index == seq_len) {
237          res.status = kMatchComplete;
238          goto reset;
239        }
240      } else {
241        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
242        goto reset;
243      }
244    }
245    s->_index = index;
246    res.status = kMatchPause;
247    res.current = p;
248    return res;
249  reset:
250    s->_index = 0;
251    res.current = p;
252    return res;
253  }
254  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_to_lower(
255      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
256      const unsigned char* endp,
257      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
258    uint32_t index;
259    llparse_match_t res;
260    index = s->_index;
261    for (; p != endp; p++) {
262      unsigned char current;
263      current = ((*p) >= 'A' && (*p) <= 'Z' ? (*p | 0x20) : (*p));
264      if (current == seq[index]) {
265        if (++index == seq_len) {
266          res.status = kMatchComplete;
267          goto reset;
268        }
269      } else {
270        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
271        goto reset;
272      }
273    }
274    s->_index = index;
275    res.status = kMatchPause;
276    res.current = p;
277    return res;
278  reset:
279    s->_index = 0;
280    res.current = p;
281    return res;
282  }

7598  enum llparse_match_status_e {
7599    kMatchComplete,
7600    kMatchPause,
7601    kMatchMismatch
7602  };
7603  typedef enum llparse_match_status_e llparse_match_status_t;
7604  struct llparse_match_s {
7605    llparse_match_status_t status;
7606    const unsigned char* current;
7607  };
7608  typedef struct llparse_match_s llparse_match_t;
7609  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_to_lower(
7610      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
7611      const unsigned char* endp,
7612      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
7613    uint32_t index;
7614    llparse_match_t res;
7615    index = s->_index;
7616    for (; p != endp; p++) {
7617      unsigned char current;
7618      current = ((*p) >= 'A' && (*p) <= 'Z' ? (*p | 0x20) : (*p));
7619      if (current == seq[index]) {
7620        if (++index == seq_len) {
7621          res.status = kMatchComplete;
7622          goto reset;
7623        }
7624      } else {
7625        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
7626        goto reset;
7627      }
7628    }
7629    s->_index = index;
7630    res.status = kMatchPause;
7631    res.current = p;
7632    return res;
7633  reset:
7634    s->_index = 0;
7635    res.current = p;
7636    return res;
7637  }
7638  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_to_lower_unsafe(
7639      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
7640      const unsigned char* endp,
7641      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
7642    uint32_t index;
7643    llparse_match_t res;
7644    index = s->_index;
7645    for (; p != endp; p++) {
7646      unsigned char current;
7647      current = ((*p) | 0x20);
7648      if (current == seq[index]) {
7649        if (++index == seq_len) {
7650          res.status = kMatchComplete;
7651          goto reset;
7652        }
7653      } else {
7654        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
7655        goto reset;
7656      }
7657    }
7658    s->_index = index;
7659    res.status = kMatchPause;
7660    res.current = p;
7661    return res;
7662  reset:
7663    s->_index = 0;
7664    res.current = p;
7665    return res;
7666  }
7667  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_id(
7668      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
7669      const unsigned char* endp,
7670      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
7671    uint32_t index;
7672    llparse_match_t res;
7673    index = s->_index;
7674    for (; p != endp; p++) {
7675      unsigned char current;
7676      current = *p;
7677      if (current == seq[index]) {
7678        if (++index == seq_len) {
7679          res.status = kMatchComplete;
7680          goto reset;
7681        }
7682      } else {
7683        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
7684        goto reset;
7685      }
7686    }
7687    s->_index = index;
7688    res.status = kMatchPause;
7689    res.current = p;
7690    return res;
7691  reset:
7692    s->_index = 0;
7693    res.current = p;
7694    return res;
7695  }

910  static llparse_state_t llhttp__internal__run(
911      llhttp__internal_t* state,
912      const unsigned char* p,

914    int match;
915    switch ((llparse_state_t) (intptr_t) state->_current) {
916      case s_n_llhttp__internal__n_closed:
917      s_n_llhttp__internal__n_closed: {
918        if (p == endp) {
919          return s_n_llhttp__internal__n_closed;
920        }
921        switch (*p) {
922          case 10: {
923            p++;
924            goto s_n_llhttp__internal__n_closed;
925          }
926          case 13: {
927            p++;
928            goto s_n_llhttp__internal__n_closed;
929          }
930          default: {
931            p++;
932            goto s_n_llhttp__internal__n_error_4;

7598  enum llparse_match_status_e {
7599    kMatchComplete,
7600    kMatchPause,
7601    kMatchMismatch
7602  };
7603  typedef enum llparse_match_status_e llparse_match_status_t;
7604  struct llparse_match_s {
7605    llparse_match_status_t status;
7606    const unsigned char* current;
7607  };
7608  typedef struct llparse_match_s llparse_match_t;
7609  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_to_lower(
7610      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
7611      const unsigned char* endp,
7612      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
7613    uint32_t index;
7614    llparse_match_t res;
7615    index = s->_index;
7616    for (; p != endp; p++) {
7617      unsigned char current;
7618      current = ((*p) >= 'A' && (*p) <= 'Z' ? (*p | 0x20) : (*p));
7619      if (current == seq[index]) {
7620        if (++index == seq_len) {
7621          res.status = kMatchComplete;
7622          goto reset;
7623        }
7624      } else {
7625        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
7626        goto reset;
7627      }
7628    }
7629    s->_index = index;
7630    res.status = kMatchPause;
7631    res.current = p;
7632    return res;
7633  reset:
7634    s->_index = 0;
7635    res.current = p;
7636    return res;
7637  }
7638  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_to_lower_unsafe(
7639      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
7640      const unsigned char* endp,
7641      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
7642    uint32_t index;
7643    llparse_match_t res;
7644    index = s->_index;
7645    for (; p != endp; p++) {
7646      unsigned char current;
7647      current = ((*p) | 0x20);
7648      if (current == seq[index]) {
7649        if (++index == seq_len) {
7650          res.status = kMatchComplete;
7651          goto reset;
7652        }
7653      } else {
7654        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
7655        goto reset;
7656      }
7657    }
7658    s->_index = index;
7659    res.status = kMatchPause;
7660    res.current = p;
7661    return res;
7662  reset:
7663    s->_index = 0;
7664    res.current = p;
7665    return res;
7666  }
7667  static llparse_match_t llparse__match_sequence_id(
7668      llhttp__internal_t* s, const unsigned char* p,
7669      const unsigned char* endp,
7670      const unsigned char* seq, uint32_t seq_len) {
7671    uint32_t index;
7672    llparse_match_t res;
7673    index = s->_index;
7674    for (; p != endp; p++) {
7675      unsigned char current;
7676      current = *p;
7677      if (current == seq[index]) {
7678        if (++index == seq_len) {
7679          res.status = kMatchComplete;
7680          goto reset;
7681        }
7682      } else {
7683        res.status = kMatchMismatch;
7684        goto reset;
7685      }
7686    }
7687    s->_index = index;
7688    res.status = kMatchPause;
7689    res.current = p;
7690    return res;
7691  reset:
7692    s->_index = 0;
7693    res.current = p;
7694    return res;
7695  }
